values:
Who the fuck is this girl?

I'd ask her to show me her relevance to this but she absolutely refuses.

This girl she is stupid stupid, but she likes to play big girl games.

This girl likes to slip her fingers into peoples heads and twine them in deep and then, when she is quite bored, she will remove them -

now there are holes.

problem is, mature neuron cells are not mitotic. 

that's it.

matter and mechanism

madness and method

O HAY JOURNAL SUP.

I YAM BOARD.

Holy motherfucker of God. If I have like 10 journals total, I would gather that there is a strong possibility of some sort of SERIOUS IDENTITY DISORDER.

So. Fux0r. Dude. Fuck. Oh my GOD.

I totally do nothing but sit on my blub butt.

I am a fucking WASTE of EPIDERMIS.

omg :<

I just want to go across teh world and like. rustle in some fucking bushes and steal some fucking french guys beret and fucking just, ugh.

Do I really have to do this?

Do I really have to grow up?
Now?
I dont want to.

But it appears I ahve no choice in the matter because its already in the works.

R U THAR GOD ITS ME LEAH.

Procrastination yields...well...this.

What is love? Oh hi, cliche philosophical question.

But really.

Is it just looking at someone and knowing they've been down the same road you have? They've felt the deepest crevices of those dark nights where there never seems to be a dawn. The space between 1am and 6am seems everlasting. Those places where you wonder if your insides can possibly collapse on themselves or can you cause yourself an aneurysm simply by very...bad...thoughts.

Maybe its just chemical. Physical. Pheromones. You just really want that person because you're biology tells you so.

Maybe you're all fucked up and you want something bad for you. Maybe you're not taking anything seriously and you don't care as long as theres a warm body next to you regardless if their heart is cold.

I'm tired of thinking of this already because there's no absolute answer for me.

I can only conclude that I don't understand a thing called love. I don't understand it one bit and I possibly don't have a clue what it is.

It could be I'm only playing house in my head and you just fit very very nicely into my version of Ken.

My heart is erratic and it pulls in so many directions. Leave. Stay. Yearn. Withdraw. Love. Hate. Disgust. Love. Love. Love. Numb.

Risky passion or an eternal best friend?

It's all so confusing.

I just know that it's so hard to love properly when you're so involved in the selfish process of developing yourself and your future.

panic courses through me at times. 
it makes me feel like my insides are crumbling.
it feels like my brain is electric and short fusing.

i feel like i'm caged.
these invisible bars you can't see but oh i feel them.
cold like metal.
stronger than anything tangible

things like these are all in my head
i want to make them all in the past

old habits die hard

ever just want to lose yourself completely?
in someone else?
in their eyes?
in their smell?
in their entirity?

ever feel tired? like you're stretched...far....too...thin

ever feel like you're too dramatic.
not dramatic enough.
too intense.
too numb.
not enough.
too much.

dream too much?
want too little?

yeah.
me too.

I'm lazy. It'll take a bit to complete my friends list.

Anyways, I've changed a lot since I first created <lj-user="violate">. Specifically in the past few months. Being away from homw has changed me, I think for the better. I'm more responsible in a lot of ways and more confident. 3 years ago I had very little self-esteem and I had no confidence in myself and no high school diploma. Now I'm nearly half way done my bachelors and pulling good grades. Most of you have met me irl at some point. Most of you knew the former me, quiet and really disjointed. 

I look forward to introducing my new perspective. I look forward to seeing the world through a new vision. I look forward to the rest of my life.

Nice to meet you, again.

/end dramatic opening.
